ver secrets.</strong> More than 100 tasty collectables are waiting. Use them to upgrade your fashion. But they are not the only secrets on this planet...</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/d94db7712fd74e0e8fd35231fbe41b5f.poster.avif?t=1758208868\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/d94db7712fd74e0e8fd35231fbe41b5f.webm?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/d94db7712fd74e0e8fd35231fbe41b5f.mp4?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>🏃‍♀️<strong> Fight bosses, run for your life.</strong> The end of (almost) every level holds a challenge. 3 Bosses to defeat and a lot of deadly traps to avoid.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/3bbe205bbfe77869823c058ce82f1e83.poster.avif?t=1758208868\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/3bbe205bbfe77869823c058ce82f1e83.webm?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/3bbe205bbfe77869823c058ce82f1e83.mp4?t=1758208868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/6e5109aa690b88d58c0668cfb3027b2a.poster.avif?t=1758208868\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139180/extras/6e5109aa690b88d58c0668cfb3027